flowchart LR
    A[Payment Success] --> B[In-transit Funds]
    B --> C[Fulfilled / Write-off]
    C --> D[Clearing Allocation]
    D --> E[Settlement Preparation / Netting]
    E --> F[Settlement Batch & Bill]
    F --> G[Accounting Posting]
    G --> H[Withdrawable Balance]
    H --> I[Payout]
    D -.-> R[Reconciliation]
    E -.-> R
    F -.-> R
    G -.-> R
